  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK664">
<l>collutal yārkku meḷiya variyavāñ </l>
<l> colliya vaṇṇañ ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To say (how an act is to be performed) is (indeed) easy for any one but far difficult it is to do according to what has been said.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
